snippet.title: TITANKIN: Prologue - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
TITANKIN: Prologue is JRPG created by a 2 person team for PC inspired by Celtic mythology, featuring visual and gameplay style pioneered by classics from the SNES and PS1 era. 

Twins Jorden and Torden are small-town miners who will soon find themselves in an adventure filled with Gods and Titans in order to find their true heritage, and what it means to be human.



For more information, and to keep up to date with the latest news keep an eye on the FerfWorks Twitter and Instagram:

https://twitter.com/ferfworks
https://instagram.com/ferfworks
